        </h2>

        {% include "homepage/_parts/benefits.twig" %}

        {% include "_snippets/homepage_separator.twig" %}

        <div class="text-center mt-5 mb-5 text-rector-green text-bigger">
            <strong>12 companies</strong> hired us this year to improve PHP code and reduce technical debt
